data.text:
Embassy Appointments

Many embassies in Germany require an appointment before you visit. On the official website of the Djibouti embassy in Berlin you will find information on opening hours and how to book appointments.

Opening hours

Please note that embassy opening hours can vary. Always contact the embassy before a visit.

Visa for Djibouti

For all Djibouti visa related matters contact the embassy in Berlin before you travel. Information is available on the embassy website () or contact the visa department by telephone (+49) 30 26 39 01 57 or email

Consulates of Djibouti in Germany

Next to the embassy in Berlin there could be additional Djibouti consulates located in Germany.

Please check below for the locations of the Djibouti consulates in Germany.
